    ☐ Longest Common Substring
        ref: [LCS](https://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/161/960229.html)
        找出最長的相同排列(無視中間不同)
        example:
            s1: a b a c d
            s2: b c d
            => b c d

        ```
            if (s1[i] == s2[j]) {
                LCS(s1[i-1], s2[j-1]) + s1[i]
            } else {
                max(LCS(s1[i], s2[j-1]), LCS(s1[i-1], s2[j]))
            }
        ```
    ☐ Longest Common Prefix
